{"tid":2368944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳媒：英財相建議一次過派500英鎊但不延長臨時援助，英國將會出現赤字4千億英鎊","createTime":"2021-01-16T15:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T08:47:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e542a82e7a5b19335371a191b59d71821235e093","tid":2368944,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570785-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570785-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=a26cd7ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570785-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=64b072d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570785-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國財相辛偉誠建議向領取失業援助的人士，一次過派發500英鎊，但不延長臨時性措施，調高現行援助金額。<br />\n<br />\n泰晤士報報道，去年新型肺炎疫情爆發初期，英國政府推行臨時措施，將援助金額每周提高20英鎊，這項措施的實施期限今年三月屆滿。報道指出，現時有6百萬英國人領取這項援助，政府就這項增加一年內支出60億英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n預計辛偉誠公布新一年財政預算的時候，英國將會出現赤字4千億英鎊。"},{"pid":"d622f7428b607cedf6700423fb390a55ab2a0aa9","tid":2368944,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"同美國一齊大重啟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fc20065fd93c124ab14ea9efef45384febcfd1","tid":2368944,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"支國又係時候份耶穌出場"},{"pid":"ccbdb0ef6f672ca8bac7cfa700cfa0fd986fb17a","tid":2368944,"uid":189234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d622f7428b607cedf6700423fb390a55ab2a0aa9","tid":2368944,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"同美國一齊大重啟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:54:06.000Z